'''Lenglinn''' is a character created specifically for ''[[The Lord of the Rings Online: Shadows of Angmar]]''. He was a [[Rangers of the North|Ranger of the North]] and part of [[Aragorn|Aragorn's]] company that helped protect the Hobbits in [[Buckland]], specifically [[Mr. Underhill]].<ref>{{VGC|SAI}} Chapter 5: The Other Riders</ref>
